Package: ggplotStudioR
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Grammar-of-Graphics Editor with Selection and Spec-Driven Codegen
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Kana", family = "Assistant", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "assistant@example.com")
Author: Kana Assistant [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kana Assistant <assistant@example.com>
Description: Provides an interactive editor for ggplot objects using Shiny,
    with click-based selection, context-aware inspection controls, a
    deterministic edit-spec model, live preview replay, and reproducible code
    export in additive and patch-script modes.
